      "content": "that makes sense. the numbers definitely look worse. one thing that's weird is that the security footage isn't showing much, like there's no obvious break-ins or anything, things just seem to vanish from the high-value bins. what are some standard ways to investigate why shrinkage is spiking if there's no clear evidence of theft?",
